Instructions
============

Podman
-------

The Dockerfile can be built using buildah as follows:

buildah build-using-dockerfile -t umec ./

To run it, use 

sudo podman run -it --rm -v /var/run/containers/storage:/var/run/containers/storage -v /var/lib/containers/storage:/var/lib/containers/storage --storage-driver=overlay --privileged=true localhost/umec bash

After this, ```podman info``` works in the container.

